  malphite: { diff: "FAVOURED", tone: "#3ddc97", tldr: "He stacks armor \u2014 your poison is magic. Proxy through him, fling his Q-slow, and laugh at his armor stack.", breakdown: "Malphite\u2019s entire defense is armor, which does nothing against your magic poison. Proxy the wave through or behind him, run him through your cloud every time he tries to CS, and E-fling him into your side when he Q-slows you. His only answer is Unstoppable Force at 6 \u2014 respect that window, then reassert.", dos: ["Proxy through him (his armor is worthless vs poison)", "E-fling him into your wave when he Q-slows you", "Track Unstoppable Force before every commit"], donts: ["Stand still for his W auto-enhancement chain", "Eat his R knockup near his team", "Sit low when his R is up"], key: { slot: "R", name: "Unstoppable Force", cd: "130s", note: "Un-dodgeable knockup. His only real power window. Respect it.", winT: "ULT DOWN", winS: "Poison-kite + fling him." }, hold: "Hold E to fling him into your wave when he Q-slows you \u2014 his armor stack is useless against your magic poison.", tip: "His armor does nothing against magic poison \u2014 proxy through him, fling his Q-slow commit, and dodge his R.", win: "Proxy (magic beats armor) and fling his Q-slow." },
